rows.label: qev093201_MSG0010
rows.name: Hey, glad to see you. How's it poppin'?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093201_MSG0100
rows.name: Ha ha! Looks like you got the hang of it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093201_MSG0110
rows.name:
Well, moving swiftly on.
Tell me...you busy right now?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093201_MSG0120
rows.name:
We're both off-duty, so...how about some pizza?
You know, from the joint downtown?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093201_MSG0130
rows.name: Huh? Why's it gotta be pizza?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093201_MSG0140
rows.name: Isn't it obvious? 'Cause it's freakin' pizza![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093201_MSG0150
rows.name:
When I first moved to America,
I must've been eating it every second day.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093201_MSG0160
rows.name:
On weekends, I'd go to bars with Doug and Lao.
Beer in one hand, piping hot slice in the other.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093201_MSG0170
rows.name:
Mmm-mm... Couldn't get enough of the stuff.
The salty pepperoni, the gooey, stringy cheese...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev093201_MSG0180
rows.name:
There was just something comforting about it,
you know? Been craving it since Earth.[ST:wait ]
